data.description: This move-in ready home has been updated from top to bottom. New kitchen, new appliances, new flooring, newer windows, new siding and roof, updated bathroom, added recessed lighting with LED lights throughout the home.  4 bedrooms and 1.5 baths. 1st floor laundry. This home has been well taken care of by the owner and is located in a great area within Altoona.
data.whatILove: This house is great comfortable home in a good location for a family.   Lots of room and storage area.    Three stories plus a walk out basement, excellent views.
